==設想通貨==
[[亞洲通貨單位|亞洲通貨單位]]被提議成一個東盟加三地區貨幣的[[加權平均|加權平均]]，并且有以此為基礎的[[亞元|亞元]]的构想。其構想受到了來自已被歐元取代的[[歐洲貨幣單位|歐洲貨幣單位]]的啟發。ACU的提議是為了穩定該地區的金融市場，不是真實貨幣，而是[[一籃子|一籃子]]東亞通貨的加權值（以GDP、貿易規模等指標加權），用以作為衡量該地區貨幣（幣值）變動的基準<ref>[http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/05/11/07/EF-481029.htm A news report of the ACU (no longer available)] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928023252/http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/05/11/07/EF-481029.htm |date=2007-09-28 }} {{zh icon}}</ref><ref>[http://www.cnfi.org.tw/kmportal/front/bin/ptdetail.phtml?Part=magazine9807-472-10 工業總會服務網 -- 亞元的未來不是夢] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119205035/http://www.cnfi.org.tw/kmportal/front/bin/ptdetail.phtml?Part=magazine9807-472-10 |date=2012-01-19 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hiram7.files.wordpress.com/2008/03/workingpaper.pdf |title=A paper analysing a broader basket of currencies |access-date=2009-05-22 |archive-date=2021-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221133426/https://hiram7.files.wordpress.com/2008/03/workingpaper.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[亞洲開發銀行|亞洲開發銀行]]正在審視和評估亞洲通貨單位的相關事務。其原定于2006年3月發布關于亞元評估的公告<ref>[http://www.vneconomy.com.vn/eng/index.php?param=article&catid=01&id=43b1548514650f Interview with Asian Development Bank representative 24/02/2006] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090313004305/http://www.vneconomy.com.vn/eng/index.php?param=article&catid=01&id=43b1548514650f |date=2009-03-13 }}</ref>。由于外部原因此番公告被推遲，而該項評估仍然在進行中<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.adb.org/AnnualMeeting/2006/EmergingMarkets/em0503-03.asp |title=ADB website: Boost for new monetary scheme - ASEAN+3 finance ministers to back Asian Currency Unit plan |access-date=2009-05-22 |archive-date=2009-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090314064751/http://www.adb.org/AnnualMeeting/2006/EmergingMarkets/em0503-03.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一個評判小組討論於2007年2月引述了阻礙亞元發展的技術上和政治上的障礙<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/nb20070222d1.html |title=The Japan Times - Japan, South Korea can pull Asia together |access-date=2009-05-22 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606155240/http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/nb20070222d1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

